metadata.description:
Unisex jacket in co-creation with [Kaftan](https://www.instagram.com/kaftancreador), the urban artist [ceroker](https://www.instagram.com/ceroker/) and the art collective [Espacio Creador](https://www.instagram.com/espacio.creador/), its versatile style allows you to remove the sleeves turning it into a vest, lined with synthetic fur rabbit , with 4 external and 2 internal pockets.  
Each jacket comes with 2 digital twins: 1 for Decentraland and 1 for The Sandbox. The airdrop will be delivered when minting is finished.
